{"tid":1189291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"69遊行 響邊度加入好","createTime":"2019-06-06T17:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T17:43:02.000Z","uid":34047,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dc94b62a313656d0dd29e09973d23ef384e71680","tid":1189291,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:19:00.000Z","msg":"年年七一 警方都會用盡辦法令遊行隊伍塞死咩<br />\n搞到啲人要暴曬 鼓燥<br />\n啲人又會就係響度叫口號叫：『開路 開路』<br />\n但根本就唔會有用<br />\n<br />\n我地呢啲良好市民就好驚有人會用以下方式打亂警渣部署：<br />\n<br />\n1. 集中一點 推開佢地啲鐵馬 等有路可以行<br />\n(唔好就係叫口號叫開路 叫到喉嚨沙都冇用)<br />\n<br />\n2. 集齊響銅鑼灣某啲位先加入 甚至一次過響外圍集合 用人海突破鐵馬加入返<br />\n<br />\n3. 響sogo集合shopping<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我諗一定人多先會有效 如果得幾個佢地實會開咪叫人快啲行唔好停留 所以諗緊響邊個位集合／加入好"},{"pid":"b69ca9145b7924c1073dec2a78a5ba487a738ee9","tid":1189291,"uid":34047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:26:31.000Z","msg":"sogo個地鐵應該會封 所以亦可以諗定響其他出口出去再去返sogo個位"},{"pid":"7064b70715dc6be5741613f0e9a21deedfa53418","tid":1189291,"uid":40628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1uYXVTx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1uYXVTx.jpg&h=4312ee21&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b870ea27ecee662ff3d63eeeaacfbb22619b800","tid":1189291,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:35:53.000Z","msg":"同問"},{"pid":"5d5862e2e32c95a666f081d0da715c95b3965002","tid":1189291,"uid":20117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:38:36.000Z","msg":"Be water by friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n封左成個地鐵站咪前後一兩個站出<br />\n多人時請善用其他交通工具<br />\n路係人行出黎既"},{"pid":"7947b637b32917c13d80346a1a35f96d2c4d8578","tid":1189291,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:39:04.000Z","msg":"同問<br />\n草地定sogo"},{"pid":"85bca73dc64973dafaec78619bb964d2dbe0f6c0","tid":1189291,"uid":153615,"like":1,"dislike":0,